    </stitle>
    <svcman/>
    <svcsubsec id="x08290199">
        <title>Crossing Gate Assembly</title>
        <svcproc svcproctype="describe" graphiccount="0">
            <title>CIRCUIT FUNCTIONS</title>
            <para>The crossing gate assembly is activated when the Red Pupil Warning Lights are activated. It is
                designed so that pedestrians are not lost in the front end blind spot by forcing them to cross in front
                of the bus with enough distance for the driver to see them.
            </para>
            <para>The assembly consists of the crossing gate, a motor and a magnet.</para>
        </svcproc>
    </svcsubsec>
